These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, librarian, chef, freelancer
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse, horse, snake
1. the freelancer is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the accountant is on the right of the freelancer##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
4. the chef is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the horse##2
6. the freelancer is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Job   | freelancer | accountant     | chef | librarian |
| Pet     | rabbit     | horse | snake  | mouse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, july, january, april
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, iced-tea, almond-milk
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Birthday   | may | july    | april     | january  |
| Beverage     | milk    | iced-tea | mirinda | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
City: rome, san-francisco, marseilles, hamburg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, ritmeester, game, bluemaster
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
3. the game-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
5. the game-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| City   | san-francisco   | marseilles   | rome  | hamburg |
| Cigar           | ritmeester | bluemaster | game | cain  |

