.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, tomato, zucchini, carrot
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, mirinda, cola
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person eating carrot is between the person eating peas and the person drinking mirinda##2
3. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
5. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Food         | tomato | peas | carrot | zucchini  |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | almond-milk   | cola  | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, davidoff, ritmeester, bluemaster
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, bellflower, marigold
1. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Cigar   | dannemann    | davidoff   | ritmeester | bluemaster    |
| Flower      | iris | zinnia | bellflower       | marigold |

