.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, pumpkin, mango, banana
4 different games are played: billiard, chess, bridge, go
1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating mango##1
2. the person playing bridge is between the person playing go and the person eating mango##2
3. the person playing billiard is between the person playing bridge and the person eating tomato##2
4. the person playing go is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Food    | tomato | mango | banana | pumpkin |
| Game   | chess | billiard  | bridge    | go  |

