.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, baccarat, chaman, vegafina
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, white, green, blue
1. the person who likes blue is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes green##1
4. the chaman-smoker is between the baccarat-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##2
5. the person who likes white is the person who likes white##1
6. the person who likes white is between the person who likes green and the vegafina-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | vegafina | chaman | baccarat     |
| Color     | pink | blue  | white   | green |

