.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, fish, dog, horse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, dubstep, classical, hip-hop
1. the fan of folk is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the owner of the horse is the fan of dubstep##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fan of classical##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
6. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Pet         | horse | dog | lizard | fish   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | classical | folk      | hip-hop |

