.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, soul, r&b, blues
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, animation, thriller
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of blues##1
4. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of soul##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fan of soul is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching adventure movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre     | electronic | soul   | r&b      | blues      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | animation | adventure | thriller |

