.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, pear, orange, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, november, april
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person eating orange is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in december##2
3. the person eating pear is the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Food   | pumpkin | pear | orange      | watermelon   |
| Birthday   | november  | december    | february | april |

