.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, black, fuchsia, light-blue
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, software-developer, social-worker, mechanic
1. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
2. the person who likes black is on the right of the software-developer##1
3. the mechanic is the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
5. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
6. the social-worker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Color       | chestnut | fuchsia | light-blue    | black      |
| Job   | social-worker       | mechanic       | software-developer | bartender |

