.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, trike, ship, scooter
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, juice, fanta
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Transport   | train     | trike  | scooter | ship |
| Beverage     | 7up | fanta | soy-milk     | juice    |

