.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, montecristo, fonseca, oliveros
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, boat, taxi
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is the davidoff-smoker##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
4. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
5. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
7. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | davidoff | fonseca  | oliveros | montecristo |
| Transport           | boat     | taxi | trike    | motorbike     |

