2. the french is on the left of the australian##1
3. the person who growssunflower is the indian##1
4. the french is the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the australian is on the left or right of the french##3
6. the australian is the person who growsiris##1
7. the french is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Flower         | sunflower | tulip | daisy | iris |
| Nationality   | indian     | canadian       | french   | australian      |

