.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, german, indian, nigerian
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, fishing, rock-climbing, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the brazilian##1
7. the indian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Nationality   | german     | brazilian     | indian          | nigerian |
| Hobby      | reading | fishing | cooking | rock-climbing  |

 